</div><table id='pages'><tr><td><span class='page_button_fade arrowButton'>&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;</span><span class='page_button_fade numberButton'>1</span><a class='numberButton' href='./page-2.html'><span class='page_button'>2</span></a><a class='numberButton' href='./page-3.html'><span class='page_button'>3</span></a><a class='numberButton' href='./page-4.html'><span class='page_button'>4</span></a><a class='numberButton' href='./page-5.html'><span class='page_button'>5</span></a><a class='numberButton' href='./page-6.html'><span class='page_button'>6</span></a><a class='numberButton' href='./page-7.html'><span class='page_button'>7</span></a><span class='page_button_fade numberButton'>...</span><a class='arrowButton' href='./page-2.html'><span class='page_button'>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;</span></a></td></tr></table><br/><a rel="nofollow" class="defBanner" href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0wv4xFYjnQy7QZFTx8v4uP" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" src="../banners/playlists/royalty-free-modern-lounge-big.webp" alt="Royalty Free Modern Lounge"></a></div><div class='bottomTextCont'><h2>Copyright-Safe Royalty-Free Music (Creative Commons Licensed)</h2>

<p><b>Free-Stock-Music.com</b> provides a curated collection of royalty-free music released under Creative Commons licenses and created by independent artists. 
The music on this website can be used in personal, commercial, and monetized projects—including YouTube videos, social media content, websites, apps, presentations, and advertisements—without copyright issues.</p>

<p>Most tracks are released under the Creative Commons license, which allows use in commercial and monetized content as long as proper artist credit is given. 
Some tracks are released under CC-BY-NC licenses, which do not allow commercial or monetized use. 
The license type for each track is clearly displayed, so users can easily confirm whether a track is suitable for monetization before using it.</p>

<p>In addition, some artists may provide specific usage terms alongside their tracks. 
For commercial or monetized projects, users should always review the artist’s stated terms. 
If no commercial restrictions are listed and the license permits commercial use, the music is safe to use for monetized and commercial content.</p>

<p>Every track includes clear licensing details and simple attribution instructions, making it easy to use the music correctly. 
When used according to the listed license and artist terms, the music can be published without worrying about copyright strikes or content claims on platforms such as YouTube, Facebook, or Instagram.</p>

<p>In the rare case of a false copyright claim—or a claim caused by missing or incorrect artist credit—our team will assist in resolving the issue by mediating between the user and the artist. 
We aim to help clear valid claims as quickly as possible so creators can continue using the music with confidence.</p>

<p>If you prefer not to credit the artist or require extended usage rights, many artists offer paid licenses directly through their official websites. 
This allows creators and businesses to choose the option that best fits their project needs.</p>

<h2>Curated Music for Every Project</h2>

<p>Whether you are creating monetized videos, advertising content, business presentations, podcasts, or personal projects, our music library is designed to support a wide range of uses. 
Each track is selected for quality, usability, and clear licensing.</p>

<p>Our mission is to provide creators with reliable, copyright-safe background music—free from hidden restrictions, confusing terms, or unexpected copyright issues.</p>

<h2>Clear Licensing. Real Artists. Safe to Use.</h2>

<p>All music on this website comes from real composers and musicians who share their work under transparent Creative Commons licenses. 
By following the listed license type and attribution requirements—or choosing a paid license when needed—you can confidently use the music across platforms while supporting the artists behind it.</p>

<p>Explore our royalty-free music playlists and find the perfect soundtrack for your next project—simple, transparent, and safe for monetization.</p>

